    "description": "&quot;<strong>Omitted</strong>&quot; is a first person psychological horror. The game takes place in an old abandoned hospital.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884800/extras/dd5472882d24c3212e12effe3402b913.poster.avif?t=1659150028\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884800/extras/dd5472882d24c3212e12effe3402b913.webm?t=1659150028\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884800/extras/dd5472882d24c3212e12effe3402b913.mp4?t=1659150028\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Environment</h2>An abandoned hospital from 1917 filled with omitted patients. The player will have to go through the dark hallways and pass next to the patients in order to regain his memory about why he is here and what is actually happening.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884800/extras/801740f32600c2e8226e14db8b871e0f.poster.avif?t=1659150028\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884800/extras/801740f32600c2e8226e14db8b871e0f.webm?t=1659150028\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1884800/extras/801740f32600c2e8226e14db8b871e0f.mp4?t=1659150028\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Storyline</h2>There is more than meets the eye when it comes to this abandoned hospital the players finds themselves in. Understanding and discovering the story will be key to beating it. There will be dark events, ideas, and a lot to discover.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay 